; Regression test for issue #576: Strange cleared report formatting (BZ#576)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/576
;
; The `cleared` report shows inconsistent formatting in the cleared balance column:
; accounts with no cleared transactions show bare "0" instead of a formatted
; amount like "$0.00", while accounts with cleared transactions show "$X.XX".

2024/01/01 * Cleared Transaction
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/02 Uncleared Transaction
    Expenses:Gas    $20.00
    Assets:Checking

test cleared
         $-30.00             $-10.00    24-Jan-01    Assets:Checking
          $30.00              $10.00                 Expenses
          $10.00              $10.00    24-Jan-01      Food
          $20.00                   0                   Gas
----------------    ----------------    ---------
               0                   0             
end test
